                    <div class="full red-text"><b data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="1250"">Hrvatski pisac, humanitarac i ambasador A1 fundraising platforme ‘Čini pravu stvar’</b></div>
                    <h2 class="full subject-intro" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="2000">Sa suprugom je pješačio gotovo 50 dana kako bi skupio 75.000 eura za potrebite</h2>
                </div>
                <figure class="half flex-responsive flex column-full-pad">
                    <img src="<?php echo $native_path ?>assets/images/bruno_big.jpg" alt="bruno Miščević">
                    <figcaption class="image-subtitle">Foto: Marko Miščević</figcaption>
